<doc id="620471" wikidata="Q345754" url="?curid=620471" title="Vengeance">
<text>Vengeance may refer to:

*Vengeance (concept) or revenge, a harmful action against a person or group in response to a grievance
== Film ==
* &quot;Vengeance&quot; (1930 film), action adventure film directed by Archie Mayo
